title: Reminiscing 2016
body:
Going through my old match history as everyone does. Except back to 2 years ago. When I really started getting into League of legends (mainly the lore side). Even though I lost this game and had no idea what I was doing it takes me back to when I just loved everything league had to offer.
Also to all those people that say they carry a game but have feeders xD

Back in 2016 when blue buff and red buff had little babies with them :(
